Types

GoBufferStream = ref object of GoStream
A kind of channel with no thread support and no size limit warning..: Like all channels, there is a risk of deadlock. Deadlock can only happen if read is not done inside a coroutine If read is done inside a coroutine, the coroutine will simply never resume, leading potentially to a memory leak (handled more or less by ORC) Source   Edit
